{"tid":1442493,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[輿論核彈+光復香港] 成立香港民衛隊，對抗警黑勾結，重建本土意識","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:35:21.000Z","uid":190579,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"790a8cf834ade924da9a36957f7d0e36d761424b","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYOKq5v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYOKq5v.jpg&h=0c4d9e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>戰略大目標: </ins></span><br />\n打<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">輿論戰</span></span>，塑迼黑衫就係善良勇敢香港人，保衛家園既形象<br />\n透過成立本土自衛隊，重建「香港人」之本土意識<br />\n對抗白色恐怖、藍色恐怖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<ins>三大原則</ins>:<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文宣！文宣！文宣！</strong></span><br />\n2) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打黑！打黑！打黑！</strong></span><br />\n3) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>減傷！減傷！減傷！</strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三大原則要係所有人既公因數<br />\n除此以外沒有底線</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span><span style=\"color: green;\">和理</span>千人大共演。勇武打黑，和理文宣，一齊減傷！<br />\n絕無大台，自己有信念，自己心存三大原則行事，自己印文宣印旗，就係香港民間衛士。<br />\n鄉黑出沒時，自發前往，現場即時組織，夠多人+少狗就可以行動<br />\n<br />\n以三大原則出發行動，以下係小弟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>十大Do and Don&rsquo;t:</ins></span><br />\n1) 勇武攻鄉黑，文宣攻警犬。鄉黑退散，警犬出動即be water，化身街坊。 (原則1,2,3) <br />\n營造鏡頭畫面: <span style=\"color: red;\">民衛隊趕走鄉黑</span> -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">警犬姍姍來遲</span> -&gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">街坊屌狗勾結鄉黑故意放水</span><br />\n2) 全部blackbloc + 包到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個樣阿媽都唔認得</span></strong></span> + 帶街坊裝換 (原則1,3) <br />\n3) 舉旗、派傳單，正義之師絕對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎影相</span></strong></span> ( 原則1 ) <br />\n<br />\n4) <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要民鬥民，對準鄉黑。</span></span></strong>不傷及無辜，不打手無寸鐵，不打女人 (原則1,2)<br />\n5) 有手無寸鐵藍絲時<span style=\"color: red;\">做戲</span>，有自己友街坊時<span style=\"color: red;\">做文</span>宣，有狗時<span style=\"color: red;\">做水</span>(或者做街坊) (原則1,2) <br />\n6) 不擋路，除非打黑，向被阻市民耐心解釋 (原則1) <br />\n7) 不與街坊對罵，唔使拗贏/趕走佢，喺鏡頭前表現得文明大方已經贏咗 (原則1)<br />\n8) 對普通市民禮貌友善 ( 原則1 )<br />\n9) 要人多！先集結後出動！人多就可以減少傷亡，如果雙方都有100個就會開打，如果我方有1000個對方就會淆底走佬，不戰而勝。 (原則3)<br />\n10) 集結時做住文宣先，市民見到咁多黑衫唔知咩料會驚 (原則1) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>文宣品:</ins></span><br />\n一定要有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">旗</span></strong></span>，比市民同記者睇到我地既行動目的<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳單</span></span></strong>，focus 1)警黑勾結 2)唔洗怕白色恐怖 3)黑衫會保護普通市民<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做媒</span></span></strong>，街坊裝唱好黑衫，接受埋記者訪問最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>上兵伐謀，其次伐交，其次伐兵，其下攻城<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">&mdash;孫子兵法</blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">&mdash;梁天琦</blockquote><br />\n</div><br />\n<blockquote>我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">&mdash;梁天琦<br />\n</div></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8156015bf7154c7b710ad287b33bc8df00759865","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oy8a57k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOy8a57k.jpg&h=b586d03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPYN8kG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPYN8kG.jpg&h=0c51fbc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bspNoT2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbspNoT2.jpg&h=57fd478c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da2f4eba9038e5ee005e506faea75933e74cc550","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554db1a9513e60382a133c8054358ce3c49d6aa9","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88edd0a05fa18b85131ac2a624947d5e8d5a0156","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ec4fd16346836927a7284a89a1daa7967481b4","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159b2fe2ca47d5880e07acd8a86e1209586d259e","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d6d034e949e33c0c47dd8b1d6fa336552971a4","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b55e77a9bfe4297dab755d537cde84c702486a0","tid":1442493,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d57ca057b00cc94f3f8f7cbd5d13235cb73f23","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c27819a884e198c8e82653bc18f96131b68986","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b55e77a9bfe4297dab755d537cde84c702486a0","tid":1442493,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"如認同請幫推"},{"pid":"cd8d9c95151870f31f522bba5d812c50f84f3f8a","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93f6a7b5791dae01869b670055ac41abdc8031c","tid":1442493,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3c27819a884e198c8e82653bc18f96131b68986","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b55e77a9bfe4297dab755d537cde84c702486a0","tid":1442493,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"如認同請幫推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"推緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04211bbf37822021c51dacab0db316919f5978d4","tid":1442493,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faf461fec5286bd32f606534d2d9dd1ab42412e","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f93f6a7b5791dae01869b670055ac41abdc8031c","tid":1442493,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3c27819a884e198c8e82653bc18f96131b68986","tid":1442493,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b55e77a9bfe4297dab755d537cde